490 f. Here, as in 475 f-., Simo is quite right in thinking the behavior of Lesbia unusual. She should have visited her patient sooner, and she should have finished her directions before leaving the house. The audience knows the explanation of both blunders : Lesbia is care- less, temeraria (229).
